Salesforce Functions Is Being Retired
Salesforce Functions is retiring on January 31, 2025. You can continue using your subscription through your existing Order Term. To preserve the capabilities that Salesforce Functions provided to your org, deploy an alternative solution before your existing Order Term ends.
